title: GOLD+ ranked 5's team (JG + TOP) 18+
body:
gidday lads and ladettes me and mi home boys adrian and kolby are looking for two players to join our serious / kinda social ranked 5's team
need a **jungler** pref challanger and no lower then diamond 5 ;).
and a brain dead **top laner**  who is mellow af and doesnt mind getting camped by the other team and tping for team fights.
add me and hit me up for an add to team ign gingeronsafari.


we look forward to hearing for you delightful sausages soon yours truly team bunnings snags
